<item>
            <title>[LU-2712] enable sanity.sh and sanityn.sh SLOW=no tests for review</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-2712</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;There are a number of tests that are skipped due to SLOW=no on &quot;review&quot; builds, but only take a minute or so.  Some only take a few seconds.  Enabling them would improve test coverage, and only increase testing times by a small fraction (10 minutes over a normal 7h test run).&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;All of the tests that will be enabled are currently passing on master for at least the past two weeks.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;There are still some tests that take tens of minutes to run for &quot;full&quot; test runs that will continue to be skipped for &quot;review&quot;.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
